The '''[[Exchange]] Shadow Caster''' was an advanced [[Stealth field generator/Legends|stealth field generator]] mounted on a [[Utility belt/Legends|utility belt]], and was manufactured and distributed by the Exchange in the period following the [[Jedi Civil War]]. It was of considerable use as an escape tool on [[Planet/Legends|planets]] where agents of the Exchange were outnumbered by local authorities.

